<div class="slide-footer"><br></div>
</section>
<section id="slide-org71fa3e1">
<h3 id="org71fa3e1">Display/Display Settings</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org71fa3e1">
</div>
<div class="slide-footer"><br></div>
</section>
<section id="slide-org4530def">
<h4 id="org4530def">Resolution</h4>
<ul>
<li>Important for LCDs and using second monitors
<ul>
<li>LCD monitors in particular have &ldquo;native&rdquo; resolutions</li>

</ul></li>

</ul>
<div class="slide-footer"><br></div>
</section>
<section id="slide-org2c0239a">
